metadata.name: Zootz 1/10
metadata.description:
ZOOTZ GENESIS EDITION

10 "Zootz" available to mint 

We all love a Zoot, so I've decided to drop the genesis edition of the series. I had pictured and envisioned this release before I had even created this track. With ongoing time constraints and issues with releases I wanted to put a new track out there but with something a lil different behind it. Enjoy the track, its even better with a Zoot! only available here: this track wont be uploaded elsewhere

Each person who holds a Zoot in there hand will be entitled to:

-the session stems in stereo wav
-the instrumental
-the acapella/vox track
-invitation to private discord and telegram group created for holders
-FULL RIGHTS TO USE THE STEMS AND/OR REMIX HOWEVER YOU LIKE.YOU FREELY USE THE CONTENT HOWEVER AND WHEREVER YOU LIKE WHETHER THAT BE MINTING ANOTHER PROJECT OR RELEASING ON DSP'S
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
if some how there is a sell out I will run each wallet through a randomiser and ONE holder will be given a folder unreleased music and the following exclusive bonuses

-*collaboration on a track or artwork for a future mint*
and/or
-*a selected bottle of single malt scotch whisky sent to you provided by "The Scottish Gantry" (I will provide ETH alternative if need be)*

Have a drink, have a Zoot...

All music written, recorded, produced
by Connor Pearson
